column18:
• Product Description
  • Style Note

  • This pair of striking sunglasses from Fluxx is definitely for the fashion-forward. Flaunt this stylish shade as you cruise through town and make heads turn.

  • Product Details

  • Lens colour: Graduating brown
    Lens type: Acrylic lens with 100% UV protection
    Frame colour: Brown
    Frame type: Plastic frame
    High bridge and fixed nose pads
    Comes in a hard case
    Warranty: 3 months against manufacturer defects

  • Material & Care

  • Acrylic lens and plastic frame
    Remove dust and grime by gently wiping the lens with the cloth

  • Size & Fit

  • Lens width: 50 mm
